{"tid":1629714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[歡迎入黎屌我]我想屌柒班和理非花生友","createTime":"2019-10-06T10:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T11:01:48.000Z","uid":26532,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a31df2924395f06d422f2140a92a44a5e7c31324","tid":1629714,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:17:09.000Z","msg":"先唔撚講陣地戰先 , 我個人覺得陣地戰仲有討論空間<br />\n但真正害撚死班勇武 / 前線真係班花生和理非<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母岩岩睇直播 , 鵝頸橋前面已經推得唔算好快<br />\n但班和理非/花生友 散步咁撚慢咁走 , 果班多數都係乜柒gear都冇,淨係得個黑色口罩<br />\n最撚離譜仲要有情侶拖撚住手走 , 拍拖咪撚去呢到場合玩啦屌<br />\n<br />\n講真用下個腦先行上去睇啦, 講撚左4個月都仲可以唔跑唔走 , 頂撚住哂前面班人<br />\n<br />\n勇武想打果陣又走撚哂, 勇武想走果時又塞撚住哂 , 和理非花生友先係害死前線既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582086b34a6dd4f1f9ea29def635cb3c43770e3d","tid":1629714,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:20:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e740f8397f5e9090b1d3835a3f47a57ed517a3fa","tid":1629714,"uid":270629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"［最新消息］全民起動 三罷民意調查<br />\n<br />\n截至10月6日下午4點，我們暫時收到超過32,000份有效回應。感謝大家支持，請繼續廣傳，全家總動員，一齊填問卷，我哋要更多，更多支持！<br />\n<br />\n請登入 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nWkSyo&d=zkxump%2FGNOlz%2FwmZAqM4lDe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=598f19ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2nWkSyo</a> 或掃QR code填寫問卷。<br />\n<br />\n民調將於10月11日中午12時結束。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TYY223b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTYY223b.jpg&h=dda65653&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea69468bcaa7cfca4c357de169ce06627d045843","tid":1629714,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1b8d5c57ef99a34da7d3e633a02fa79e03b5c66a","tid":1629714,"uid":302501